{
  "stem": "10397.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it was a social life in-- in-- in a limited way, because everybody worked very hard.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Saturday.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Saturday evening, that's the time to have-- we had-- everybody had a girlfriend.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Not-- many-- many boys had a girlfriend.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I had a girlfriend.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And there was there, in Prague, the Jewish life was concentrated in a Jewish center, Cafe Ash, A-S-H, in the old part of-- of Prague.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The historical part of Prague.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And was once a complex, and in the basement was a big movie, [?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Roxie, ?] I remember.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "There was a big cafe and a restaurant, and rooms for functions-- for functions, where all kind of organizations, including our corporation, we just made a reservation.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we had to order one beer.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Nobody could-- not everybody could afford more than one beer, because it was every Saturday.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It wasn't custom.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It was not compulsory.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And then we talked.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We had, always, a speaker, you know, [?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Jean ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Baptiste. ?] He was, at that time, the number one speaker, I remember.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And we had exercises with swords, like the German corporations, but it was just, you know, to keep up the tradition of the fighting corporation.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And we were singing Zionist, Jewish songs, and German songs, Polish songs.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We had, also, students from Latvia, and Lithuania, Estonia, and [INAUDIBLE] and Lithuanian, yeah.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Latvia, Lithuania, Estonia.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And-- and so, everybody-- there were some students who were living on $15 a month, like me, and some students lived on $10 a month.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "At that time, it was $15 was middle class, $10 was poor.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And some-- maybe some students, who were very few, had more money.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "But the more money they had, the less they did studying.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My parents.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I didn't work.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1937.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I went home.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
